OL,3,CSheep mauled by dog put down leaving
OL,4,Cshepherd 'devastated'
OL,6,FA shepherd has been left "devastated"
OL,7,Fafter one of her sheep had to be put
OL,8,Fdown following a dog attack.
OL,10,FVera Hoenan, who runs a farm in
OL,11,FOxfordshire, says it is the latest in
OL,12,Fa string of attacks on her livestock.
OL,14,FThe injured ewe was treated by an
OL,15,Femergency vet, but had to be put down
OL,16,Fas it was too distressed.
