OL,3,CSheep mauled by dog put down leaving
OL,4,Cshepherd 'devastated'
OL,6,FVera Hoenan said: "It's devastating,
OL,7,Fit's absolutely devastating. I have a
OL,8,Fvery small flock, they all have names,
OL,9,Fthey're all tame, they come when
OL,10,Fcalled, so you have a relationship
OL,11,Fwith them much in the same way as you
OL,12,Fhave with your family dog.
OL,14,F"So to find her with such extensive
OL,15,Finjuries, including enormous amount of
OL,16,Fpain, it's devastating."
OL,18,FThe incident, on 24 April 2025, left
OL,19,Fother sheep in her flock injured
OL,20,Fcosting her #1,000 in vet bills.
