OL,3,CSheep mauled by dog put down leaving
OL,4,Cshepherd 'devastated'
OL,6,FIt is the second time a member of her
OL,7,Fflock has died from a dog attack, but
OL,8,Fthey have been left scared and injured
OL,9,Fmany more times.
OL,11,FDespite signs warning people to keep
OL,12,Ftheir dogs on a lead, Vera encounters
OL,13,Fabout 20 dogs a week who have been
OL,14,Fallowed to run free.
OL,16,FWhen she has asked dog owners to put
OL,17,Ftheir pets on a lead, she has been
OL,18,Fverbally abused.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
