OL,3,CSheep mauled by dog put down leaving
OL,4,Cshepherd 'devastated'
OL,6,FShe said: "Sadly I've been assaulted
OL,7,Fmultiple times in the last year as
OL,8,Fwell, as a result of telling people
OL,9,Fthey're on private land and their dog
OL,10,Fneeds to be on a lead.
OL,12,F"A lot of people don't realise the
OL,13,Fimpact their dog can have and, as a
OL,14,Fresult, they think they can get away
OL,15,Fwith just letting their dog off lead.
OL,17,F"But even a small dog can chase sheep
OL,18,Fand run them hard, so any dog can do
OL,19,Fit and the people don't always react
OL,20,Fas nicely as they could."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
