OL,6,FIn a recent survey, the National Sheep
OL,7,FAssociation found:
OL,9,FNathan Boyd, National Farmers' Union
OL,10,FSouth, said: "NFU Mutual have said in
OL,11,Ftheir latest report that in 2023 they
OL,12,Fsaw #2.3 million of livestock killed
OL,13,For seriously injured through livestock
OL,14,Fworrying.
OL,16,F"Those figures are 30% up on the year
OL,17,Fbefore. We know it's a big issue. We
OL,18,Fknow police forces are working hard to
OL,19,Fcombat this.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
