OL,3,CSheep mauled by dog put down leaving
OL,4,Cshepherd 'devastated'
OL,6,F"The concerns are that much more of
OL,7,Fthis goes on that isn't reported where
OL,8,Fdogs are let off leads, they worry
OL,9,Flivestock, and people think there's no
OL,10,Fintended consequences and people
OL,11,Faren't around to see it, when actually
OL,12,Flong term we see ewes aborting and
OL,13,Fdying through stress."
OL,15,FVera believes vets, dog groomers and
OL,16,Fschools should all help educate dog
OL,17,Fowners of the rules.
