OL,4,Cshepherd 'devastated'
OL,6,FIn a statement, a spokesperson from
OL,7,FThames Valley Police, said: "On 24
OL,8,FApril this year, between 4pm and
OL,9,F5.15pm, on Highworth Road, Watchfield,
OL,10,FFaringdon, a sheep was attacked by a
OL,11,Fdog and sadly died.
OL,13,F"We are appealing to anybody who has
OL,14,Fdash-cam, CCTV or doorbell camera
OL,15,Ffootage that has captured the incident
OL,16,Fto please contact us.
OL,18,F"You can make a report via our website
OL,19,For by calling 101, quoting crime
OL,20,Freference number 43250199751.
